886
01:49:49,423 --> 01:49:50,423
Orangmu?

887
01:49:53,969 --> 01:49:54,969
Atau orangmu.

888
01:50:00,893 --> 01:50:03,437
Kita lindungi burung layang.

889
01:50:07,858 --> 01:50:08,858
Bersama.

